"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月25日消息，日本国家税务局更新了加密货币准则，解决了包括质押和加密货币借贷在内的问题。但该机构没有提到NFT或代币空投--这表明它目前不认为NFT交易或空投需要纳税。该机构指出，在进行税收计算时，需要以法币日元计算。\",\"timestamp\":1640412011,\"title\":\"日本税务机构更新加密货币准则，适用于质押借贷，但不适用NFT\"},\"digest\":\"bhsbVFB4aLWGtB0cqch4KJSoNGE837s7YRpQxb_R9_s\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x373bD502Da89fdb49667E2c24213c00d90fBf3BC\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"IEgzB8LyKikAvKsLKzofgXuKjLOFEQO8bJjyJ0r9Yhw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"USTbZjUlfvo7qTnJS71k302eUk8ezPFu9aD5qQu34YI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"OD3ZNsLaYsPc4shUY72dPVMPZidc5iHgYMC76aPL1TGvEt-sRSDxjCC8Sh9GeTLsSPpYDLaYzDKWfNeyn1alEg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xe5703d45f2a0e26af4a84141b728c5ca8319cdff8cabe1b494e2f847bf6e5a0e78c5e57b7da5efa6516db6186f7c89d676effb9e73ab3b502850b36cea8470cc1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"IEgzB8LyKikAvKsLKzofgXuKjLOFEQO8bJjyJ0r9Yhw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"USTbZjUlfvo7qTnJS71k302eUk8ezPFu9aD5qQu34YI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"bhsbVFB4aLWGtB0cqch4KJSoNGE837s7YRpQxb_R9_s\"}"